<HEADLINE>
<P>
POSTCARDS FROM THE EDGE OF HELL; SARAJEVO: SHELLS FALL AGAIN, ELECTRICITY 
FALTERS AND WATER TRICKLES. ARTISTS' POSTERS SHRINK AND COLORS DISAPPEAR. 
