initially left her paralyzed, was named the winner of the Honda Inspiration 
Award, which goes to the collegiate woman athlete who has overcome a handicap 
to contribute to her team. . . . Sunny Garcia of Hawaii is the overall leader 
after the first round of the $155,000 Surf Classic in Australia. 
</P>
