<P>
ATHLETE OF THE WEEK: GIRLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Julia Feldman 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Taft 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Tennis 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Senior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: A three-year varsity performer who played No. 1 singles 
the past two seasons, Feldman finished 21-0 and capped the season by winning 
the City Section singles championship Friday.A powerful and athletic 
serve-and-volley player, Feldman finished 48-2 in three years. 
