</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other nonleague girls' games: 
</P>
<P>
 Ocean View 2, Huntington Beach 1 -- Kim Engesser scored two second-half goals 
to rally visiting Ocean View (5-1). Megan Waters scored for Huntington Beach 
(3-2-1). 
</P>
