From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Federated Sets Date for Merger: The department store chain said it aims to 
close its proposed merger with R.H. Macy & Co. on Monday. Under the plan, the 
combined company would issue about 55.6 million shares of common stock and 
about 18 million warrants to Macy's unaffiliated creditors. Federated said any 
change in the proposed closing date could affect the number of shares and 
warrants issued. 
</P>
