parcels under 10 ounces) Fourth Class (parcels) .871 .740 .760 .663 .626 .674 
.615 **** 
</P>
<P>
 Down the Chute 
</P>
<P>
 The average American household gets more than 21 pieces of mail each week -- 
the majority of which consists of advertising materials. 
</P>
<P>
 Pieces per household per week: First-class: 9.23 Second-class: 1.60 
Third-class: 9.97 Fourth-class: 0.06 Government: 0.40 **** 
</P>
<P>
